# Database

- Prisma schema is the single source of truth for data model.
- All migrations via `prisma migrate dev` — never hand-edit applied migrations.
- No raw SQL in application code.
- Career Library is canonical — resumes are generated exports, not primary storage.
- Index foreign keys and frequently queried columns.
- Seed scripts in `prisma/seed.ts` for dev data and AI model configs.
